The Outlast Trials is coming to Xbox Series S/X, Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and PlayStation 5 on March 5th, 2024 
Pre-order on PlayStation → https://store.playstation.com/en-ca/product/UP2113-PPSA05003_00-0964993366721710
Pre-order on Xbox → https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/the-outlast-trials/9nr13rf1v2wv

The Outlast Trials, is a brand new take on the acclaimed Outlast survival horror series, set in the same terrifying universe as the previous titles, only this time you can choose to play on your own or with friends in a team of up to four people.

Thanks to all the Outlast fans, content creators, and streamers who played, screamed, and survived the Trials (or died trying to survive, that's ok too, you're getting there!) our team at Red Barrels is grateful to all our fans and Reagents for going on this ride with us! Can't wait to see many new faces enter The Outlast Trials on console!

